From: Howard Chen <howard.chen@linaro.org>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2015 11:56:06 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] drivers: cpuidle: Refine ARM64_CPUIDLE options to support
 multiple drivers

This patch adds a selection to the CPU_IDLE_MULTIPLE_DRIVERS for
ARM64_CPUIDLE.

Signed-off-by: Howard Chen <howard.chen@linaro.org>
---
 drivers/cpuidle/Kconfig.arm | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/cpuidle/Kconfig.arm b/drivers/cpuidle/Kconfig.arm
index 21340e0..f521448 100644
--- a/drivers/cpuidle/Kconfig.arm
+++ b/drivers/cpuidle/Kconfig.arm
@@ -4,6 +4,7 @@
 config ARM_CPUIDLE
         bool "Generic ARM/ARM64 CPU idle Driver"
         select DT_IDLE_STATES
+	select CPU_IDLE_MULTIPLE_DRIVERS
         help
           Select this to enable generic cpuidle driver for ARM.
           It provides a generic idle driver whose idle states are configured
